{"tid":536703,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唐詩詠奪視后，再次體現連登仔質素。","createTime":"2018-01-22T05:12:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T07:14:25.000Z","uid":31552,"like":34,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6b2f668282ea0e11a97dc0fdcd0b0792649fd96e","tid":536703,"uid":31552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T05:12:06.000Z","msg":"之前又講到唐詩詠點點點 好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜加？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n[清泉][多圖]唐詩詠真係好撚柒正<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/233192/page/1?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/233192/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n同埋你地又知係佢自己本人買LIKE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\nTBB不嬲鐘意內定架啦，第一日睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n只能夠講，真係好多連登仔都好撚柒 人屌你又屌。逢紅必反呢個「文化」真係好撚好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n題外話。<br />\n<br />\n同時最近既post都好能夠睇到某部份連登仔質素有幾咁低。唔係女又J圖，認真post又比人屌假膠。總知唔係女既post都甚少有回應。<br />\n<br />\n不過上連登真係勿認真。<br />\n<br />\n因為上到黎，所有女都係臭雞。連登仔係至尊無上既大判官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係連登仔既世界佢地係最撚型，所有衣著服飾髮型都係MK、偽韓、毒撚。真係好想知連登仔係咪和尚無頭髮。<br />\n<br />\n要數連登醜陋之處真係幾多字都講唔曬。<br />\n大概重點既都講曬。<br />\n希望大家唔好因爲「匿名」講野行為唔好咁不負責任。真係好撚嘔心。<br />\n<br />\n利申：愈黎愈少上連登，所以唔洗趕住叫我走。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd835a82a3e317b9e7b4623ee1cfc2eaec46f998","tid":536703,"uid":38539,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T05:38:46.000Z","msg":"咁公道講句，應該兩班人嚟，<br />\n正評個班只係純粹外觀欣賞，<br />\n罵唐詩詠個班係八婆師奶格，<br />\n典型的TVB觀眾，亦可能係其他藝員死忠，<br />\n自己女神無獎咪罵囉"},{"pid":"e7196fe28dbb7b16441383fb63f03d479ccf6b5d","tid":536703,"uid":31552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T06:16:40.000Z","msg":"其實真係好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fafa3e2e2278788c99227d7bf5ef4508dbb6ea5","tid":536703,"uid":31552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T06:39:20.000Z","msg":"不過通常開親呢啲post，啲低質連登仔都唔會正視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d074debe1ad9086d25ed66ceb3c32a1f1f5030aa","tid":536703,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T06:41:52.000Z","msg":"因為2個慨念想撞而炒車"},{"pid":"b9038a51557b9af2fb55474620da3e69fe913d84","tid":536703,"uid":31552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d074debe1ad9086d25ed66ceb3c32a1f1f5030aa","tid":536703,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T06:41:52.000Z","msg":"因為2個慨念想撞而炒車"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T07:20:20.000Z","msg":"小心比肥絲捉字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07515a05896497a45e339ed005b84d611f53f01d","tid":536703,"uid":31552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T07:42:54.000Z","msg":"連登仔成日自打嘴巴真係好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f29e790cd1f8fb66b53845cd8f1bd50bb9b20718","tid":536703,"uid":85099,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T07:46:33.000Z","msg":"唐詩穎係好正，好想瘋狂奶佢對腳同佢做愛。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但唔覺得佢應該拎視后lor, 佢未夠班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef4fe6ea910c8516a950cc094019bddd4c3bbab","tid":536703,"uid":31552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f29e790cd1f8fb66b53845cd8f1bd50bb9b20718","tid":536703,"uid":85099,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T07:46:33.000Z","msg":"唐詩穎係好正，好想瘋狂奶佢對腳同佢做愛。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但唔覺得佢應該拎視后lor, 佢未夠班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T09:09:14.000Z","msg":"都係個句啦，tbb咪姐係好似社會縮影咁囉。<br />\n無線獨大，收視唔怕無。所以係道嘈都係曬氣，何況，真係佢自己買like咩屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df60c51195cabf5197e03d561d3b58974bdef53f","tid":536703,"uid":31552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T09:14:33.000Z","msg":"話左呢啲post一定無乜人理，因為駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37ca5961dd1488c29cd1869e6ff90ac3221bbc1","tid":536703,"uid":31552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T09:59:40.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9ea4ad0f415d05cf8cfc7ba89d4665835d8f872","tid":536703,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T10:03:19.000Z","msg":"連登狗已經縮返入狗閪度唔敢出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7268919d9b9330f711ce925be600e846d4148708","tid":536703,"uid":31552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9ea4ad0f415d05cf8cfc7ba89d4665835d8f872","tid":536703,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T10:03:19.000Z","msg":"連登狗已經縮返入狗閪度唔敢出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T11:41:36.000Z","msg":"仲以為會有人駁我..點知..?"},{"pid":"c4ecdd629b0407f43ecea643c52af73ad02ef517","tid":536703,"uid":81256,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T11:50:59.000Z","msg":"白鳩痴<br />\n成個連登咁多人<br />\n只可以有一種睇法？<br />\n你諗野同共產黨一撚樣"},{"pid":"70a21b55bbc680bb301c6fe1dc1cef0d14960882","tid":536703,"uid":67903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9038a51557b9af2fb55474620da3e69fe913d84","tid":536703,"uid":31552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d074debe1ad9086d25ed66ceb3c32a1f1f5030aa","tid":536703,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"reply